# vendiOS lock screen — fingerprint-only PAM service.
#
# vendilock runs this as a second, parallel transaction so you can swipe to
# unlock at any time. The password path uses the default (login) stack and is
# entirely independent, so a missing/failed swipe never blocks typing the
# passphrase. A fingerprint match satisfies "sufficient" and the stack returns
# success; anything else falls through to pam_deny and fails quietly.
auth     sufficient  pam_fprintd.so
auth     required    pam_deny.so
account  required    pam_permit.so
